headline: Is General Dynamics (GD) Still Attractive After A 38.8% One Year Share Price Rise
summary: If you are wondering whether General Dynamics shares still offer value at around US$365.83, you are not alone. This article walks through what that price actually implies. The stock has seen a 6.4% gain over the last 30 days. The 1 year return of 38.8% and 5 year return of 171.1% sit against a modest 0.8% pullback over the past week and a 6.5% return year to date.
